This is a BZR plugin for play framework, just build the framework after pull
* run the ant script every time updating your play repository *

HOW TO :

create ~/.bazaar/plugins if it not exists

cd ~/.bazaar/plugins

git clone https://waxzce@github.com/waxzce/BZR-plugin-for-play-framework.git playbzr

!! your directory name does not contains any "-"

now you can check if the plugin is here by 
bzr plugins


have fun and report for problems
-> we don't support any bugs on windows

